T1  - The Delivery and Control of Quality in Supplier-Producer Contracts
AU  - Reyniers, Diane J.
AU  - Tapiero, Charles S.
Y1  - 1995/10/01
PY  - 1995
DA  - 1995/10/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.41.10.1581
